白鹿洞书院</span></a></div></li><li><div class="CM-vertical"  node-type="list"><div class="vertical"><a href="http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2018-04-23/doc-ifznefki0696482.shtml" target="_blank" class="img"><img node-type="img"  _src="http://n.sinaimg.cn/translate/200/w600h400/20180422/8uHB-fznefkh8712057.jpg" style="width: 100%;height: 100%;" /></a></div><a href="http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2018-04-23/doc-ifznefki0696482.shtml" target="_blank" class="txt"><span class="ellipsis" title="千年学府 石鼓书院">千年学府 石鼓书院</span></a></div></li><li><div class="CM-vertical"  node-type="list"><div class="vertical"><a href="http://news.sina.com.cn/o/2018-05-18/doc-iharvfhv0116498.shtml" target="_blank" class="img"><img node-type="img"  _src="http://n.sinaimg.cn/translate/95/w550h345/20180518/8NNH-harvfhv0116032.jpg" style="width: 100%;height: 100%;" /></a></div><a href="http://news.sina.com.cn/o/2018-05-18/doc-iharvfhv0116498.shtml" target="_blank" class="txt"><span class="ellipsis" title="岳麓书院：千年弦歌不绝">岳麓书院：千年弦歌不绝</span></a></div>        </li></ul>
    </div>
